{"tid":1648762,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【我地需要改善】現時狀態分析 + 少量建議","createTime":"2019-10-12T10:55:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-12T15:07:06.000Z","uid":175870,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"2280a25fa0e2a9046d73d8379b908ad32a44964a","tid":1648762,"uid":175870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T10:55:31.000Z","msg":"最近文宣混亂及不足+抗爭者出現疲態<br />\n我地需要一啲轉變<br />\n<br />\n而家我哋面對嘅問題：<br />\n<br />\n。<strong><ins><span style=\"color: violet;\">活動太突發 + 過多活動</span></ins></strong><br />\n<strong>導致：</strong>文宣混亂 + 增加疲倦感 + 分散左人數及傳媒關注<br />\n<strong>解釋：</strong>  <br />\n&gt; <ins><strong>文宣跟唔切</strong></ins><br />\n<blockquote>     <span style=\"font-size: small;\">  //一兩個突發活動都可以跟得切<br />\n跟唔切&gt;少人&gt;危險+效果差//</span> </blockquote><br />\n<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: small;\">//<span style=\"color: red;\">一單黑材料需要時間發酵</span> 文宣要時間<br />\n      當每日有活動時 <ins>好容易會蓋過左黑材料</ins>//</span></blockquote><br />\n&gt; <ins><strong>容易令人感到疲倦</strong></ins><br />\n<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: small;\">//休息係需要既(但我唔係休息撚)<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">但太多活動時, 大家既参與度唔同,<br />\n令到休息日都唔同, 最後次次活動都人少</span>//</span></blockquote><br />\n&gt;<ins><strong>分散左人數 及 傳媒關注</strong></ins><br />\n<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: small;\">//分散人數不詳述//</span></blockquote><br />\n   <blockquote> <span style=\"font-size: small;\">// 以和你X活動為例,<br />\n   <span style=\"color: red;\">和你X系列係主要突顯和理非力量既時間</span><br />\n     (咁當然都有機會演變成衝突 但我講緊重心都係和理非)<br />\n   若係有衝突既日子舉行和你X,<br />\n     <ins><span style=\"color: red;\">被搶fo &gt; 導致成個效果減低</span></ins>//</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大家須要知道活動夠多人,咁出黎既人先可以<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">感受到凝聚力</span></strong><br />\n從而有力繼續抗爭<br />\n如果係你出到黎見到小貓2 3隻, 一次兩次都係咁<br />\n你都心淡喇,仲會質疑個日程表都唔係真係有活動既<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">慢慢日程表/我地既號召力就會下降</span></ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n哩個PO講既野都係綜合大家意見+本人愚見打既<br />\n有咩講得唔好 請大家見諒+提出意見<br />\n<br />\n我會係下面幾個COMMENT再打其他野"},{"pid":"cece371181341023c1e19c1f94608ad0818b3c97","tid":1648762,"uid":175870,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T10:58:08.000Z","msg":"建議:<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>1) 減少突發活動</ins></strong><br />\n<ins>!留意!</ins>唔係取消<br />\n(明白突發活動係戰術既一種)<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">唔可以將日日突發活動變成日常</span></strong><br />\n咁樣同redbull一樣 開頭好精神<br />\n之後chur盡後冇晒力(<span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>現時狀況</ins></span>)<br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong>2) 活動分開日子搞</strong></ins><br />\n集中人數既話 力量都會較大<br />\n愈多人做和理非既活動&gt; 迴響較大,凝聚力提升&gt; 得以繼續推動抗爭運動<br />\n勇既活動唔洗講, 一定係人多安全<br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong>3) 増加文宣</strong></ins><br />\n關於文宣(整圖)既形式,<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"> 強烈建議</span></strong></span>大家睇睇:<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1438967/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1438967/page/1</a><br />\n但個人認為而家<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">最重要係淺黃/唔理解私了,裝修既人</span></strong><br />\n另外都係個幾句<br />\n-連儂牆<br />\n-Twitter<br />\n-FB (特別有親戚個D)<br />\n-IG <br />\n-Airdrop<br />\n-傳單(其實較有效,但危險,所以唔建議)<br />\n-最好就去邊都痴一張(我知好難)"},{"pid":"e4909179574859b0d7529bcd9136bf5108085b28","tid":1648762,"uid":279090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T10:58:41.000Z","msg":"其實除左呢幾樣之外有一樣野<br />\n就係和理非冇乜覺悟<br />\n兄弟可以嘅話幫我推推<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n和理非唔入就唔好話自己抗爭拉<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1648711\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1648711</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4177d0e2c1485303b6519ca211b08c526d58423b","tid":1648762,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T10:59:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6db6b4ccd0089ea6cdcfb2ac379baca2d4d4427c","tid":1648762,"uid":175870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:00:13.000Z","msg":"以下開放大家討論下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有咩好建議比大家就集中Quote哩到喇<br />\n我唔想我推PO推到冇人見到大家既留言<br />\n<br />\n覺得好既就quote 唔好既唔洗理"},{"pid":"fcfc15dc6349397d9365aaeaa38e50e25d7ed250","tid":1648762,"uid":175870,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:02:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AAYvwgK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAAYvwgK.jpg&h=0636be6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大家睇下日程表<br />\n首先辛苦文宣既手足整出黎<br />\n但真係好似有啲亂同多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8900c0d6afebb5d46da4528ce5b08e1e9dd8b2b1","tid":1648762,"uid":175870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:03:22.000Z","msg":"有好建議既就可以quote下#5<br />\n等其他人易睇啲 易討論啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8ca113179ab9aac9394970c3407b0fe81e9ccb5","tid":1648762,"uid":175870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e4909179574859b0d7529bcd9136bf5108085b28","tid":1648762,"uid":279090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T10:58:41.000Z","msg":"其實除左呢幾樣之外有一樣野<br />\n就係和理非冇乜覺悟<br />\n兄弟可以嘅話幫我推推<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n和理非唔入就唔好話自己抗爭拉<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1648711\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1648711</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:04:38.000Z","msg":"唉 如果連哩啲少少都唔做<br />\n軍心就會散晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a995051ddd709a73d188be5ad29c4cdaefed9de7","tid":1648762,"uid":175870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:04:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e595fb6db963f57f18ee535b6c4b072d322b76cf","tid":1648762,"uid":175870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:06:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a709776ca471b7dc5f1afd4154b453272a1e1aa2","tid":1648762,"uid":93248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:06:10.000Z","msg":"推動BLIZZCON國際戰線要錢要人呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1647163/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1647163/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"bc4e230e9c72bfc5e8a15d62980d4798e1f308b4","tid":1648762,"uid":175870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:07:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d2856581a3870e5060aaa60806e490f22bb8b172","tid":1648762,"uid":175870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:08:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"84ac7d0df9caf0245663de80f1fce594ad90d80a","tid":1648762,"uid":175870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:08:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6e8e3b2d40ed384cbaec751d17d6dfc4ef20ddaf","tid":1648762,"uid":263814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:14:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2gFawme.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2gFawme.png&h=7eadedfc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e252a625db5ed44e17f962e38afd2fa7316f9405","tid":1648762,"uid":175870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:15:11.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"49bfc021e87763ec6581c1210d66b93430940292","tid":1648762,"uid":166659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:18:45.000Z","msg":"推啊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nsMQwnu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnsMQwnu.jpg&h=66be91e2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"02babf439a5bbbcf39634c6789fa045fe541f1c2","tid":1648762,"uid":175870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:24:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1d1846f2a5e3bc048bf03c125bcd073a38f8703b","tid":1648762,"uid":252973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:24:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8114ff94b26f881c955bcd0a5e0d19bb6a649b74","tid":1648762,"uid":9542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:35:51.000Z","msg":"以下精簡啲唔打太長<br />\n<br />\n1. 活動目標: 往往欠奉或力度不夠，要有<span style=\"color: red;\">緊貼香港或國際形勢</span> (如今個星期要配合支那欺壓西方社會價值)或要有<span style=\"color: red;\">迫切性</span>(如市民如何受支那港共黑警威脅/可以關注返民生議題，警暴好多人已經好麻目)<br />\n<br />\n2. 文宣/論述: 呢樣同目標好有關連，我地既<span style=\"color: red;\">論述欠缺內容深度，難以鼓動民眾/爭取更多支持</span>，但其實我地應該有好多知識份子/好多留意新聞作分析既人，<span style=\"color: red;\">要突顯我地同弱智藍絲有唔同，就要展示我地既深度</span>(如呢個星期無乜統一展示支共對全人類既實際政經社文國際各方面威脅，點解運動/民主重要) (又如其實呢十年國際民主陣營衰退，好多中產支持極權解決社會混亂多於民主，但無人傾過可以點做文宣)<br />\n<br />\n3. 形式: 唔一定日日，但個個星期要有活動，但<span style=\"color: red;\">唔一定係傳統遊行</span>(如展示黑警罪證流動展覽式遊行remind 香港人佢地每人每日都受政府/警察威脅)<br />\n<br />\n4. 策略轉型: 要打長久戰先可以收港共皮，但唔一定要傳統衝突先做到，<span style=\"color: red;\">必要時要配合到時勢發展作唔同形式轉型</span>(如黎近既區選用唔同方式集中打擊各區每一隻建制狗，為長遠立法會選戰作準備)<br />\n<br />\n5. 活動時間/數量: 我地無大台，但要善用民眾同民主既優勢，可以比<span style=\"color: red;\">群眾投票</span>，揀最多個一兩個選擇就去馬，較低成本又較有效率收集民意，到底想要咩既活動同幾時既活動，又可以減少有少數既鬼影響主流民意<br />\n <br />\n6. 最後如果運動輸既話一定唔係因為港共打壓/示威者出現疲態/文宣不足等等，而係我地既<span style=\"color: red;\">創意不足/欠缺改變</span>，往往一個策略用得好就唔變，除左動員唔到足夠人同我地打呢場仗，仲次次都比港共針對打擊，運動初期有好多策略，搞到港共好頭痕，但我地明顯已經技窮，文宣次次形式地點時間一樣，但欠缺實質內容<br />\n<br />\n7. 其他: 除非好重要好突發，但<span style=\"color: red;\">一般活動申請宣傳要set 截止時間</span>(如前一日下午6點前)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">要記住，呢場運動如果輸，一定唔係輸敵人打壓，而係輸我地自己一成不變！！</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"c29841c7cf229819626233680fe0629219c88639","tid":1648762,"uid":175870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:44:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cc92857b2b56c27c2beb889ae1610830e9573756","tid":1648762,"uid":175870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:44:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"442ce30a2521a357b8183c244f46d9f6129a7ec6","tid":1648762,"uid":50904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:46:34.000Z","msg":"為左拋磚引玉我都寫左啲關於出圖嘅建議，不過太長唔copy黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不如一齊入去傾下有無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>[重開]有效文宣方程式:激起情緒-&gt;引導-&gt;行動呼籲</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1648823/\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1648823/</a>"},{"pid":"4e73cd64b8c973e59a1ae746f2da979a5c1eb21c","tid":1648762,"uid":175870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:49:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cf65a9649e25050f16dbeea88f78e3bdbe2aa65a","tid":1648762,"uid":175870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:51:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5e34ebc90b3d4775eaa05e4b1ee0cdd699661657","tid":1648762,"uid":175870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:53:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bb85d02610733d9613ee8e82516d4e37d2f0f0ad","tid":1648762,"uid":175870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T12:00:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"956b60bb79c606aa79e53b624ce11cc4b8323216","tid":1648762,"uid":9542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T12:06:03.000Z","msg":"認真post 無人理，仲唔係輸自己咁係輸邊個，香港人早d 收皮啦不如<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0026aa375668d759a3f038e942ae68c5e2cc513f","tid":1648762,"uid":36134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T12:11:07.000Z","msg":"而家五六日一基本都有活動<br />\n其實都幾chur <br />\n仲要持續左幾個月"},{"pid":"195ea2476b32bb1dfd767752d085ac891bfb759d","tid":1648762,"uid":271497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T12:11:19.000Z","msg":"覺得活動好亂既人入一入黎<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1648839\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1648839</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2a04258abb884e686c36384055a8250eb7e211c0","tid":1648762,"uid":175870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T12:11:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"adc245e48b4